p.d: In order to save the Oberwies building project, Rossi, the federal prosecutor, concludes an agreement with the investor Al-Baroudi and wants the case closed as quickly as possible. Directed by: Pierre Monnard (season 1, Switzerland, 2017) Screenplay: Béla Batthyany, Alexander Szombath, Dave Tucker, Andreas Stadler, Moritz Gerber Cast: Sarah Spale (Rosa Wilder), Marcus Signer (Manfred Kägi), Andreas Matti (Paul Wilder), Ruth Schwegler (Christine Wilder), László I. Kish (Robert Räber), Emanuela von Frankenberg (Béatrice Räber), Sabina Schneebeli (Barbara Rossi), Christian Kohlund (Armon Todt), Amira El Sayed (Amina al-Baroudi) Genre: detective
